data.name: btOriGuid.ToolTip
data.value:
Changing the Sim Type does not actually change the NPC type, to do that you must change the Original GUID to the NPC Template.
USE WITH CARE, if the Sim Species does not suit the NPC type the sim will get badly messed up

data.name: lbSplitChar.Text
data.value: This Sim's Character may be Split into two or more files

data.name: lbSplitChar.ToolTip
data.value: Split character files work OK in Game but SimPe can't load both parts so it doesn't handle them well..
